(54, 1, '2018-01-22 09:30:52', '2018-01-22 11:30:52', 'You\'re growing up fast, Morty. You\'re going into a great big thorn straight into my ass. It’s a new machine. It detects stuff all the way up your butt. I wish that shotgun was my penis. Sometimes science is a lot more art, than science. A lot of people don\'t get that.\r\n\r\nHe threatened to turn me in to the government, so I made him and the government go away! Do you know how many characters there are in the Simpsons Morty? There\'s like a-a billion characters, M-Morty. There was an episode where Former President BUSH was their neighbor! Sometimes science is a lot more art, than science. A lot of people don\'t get that. I\'m Mr. Crowbar, and here is my friend, who is also a crowbar!\r\n\r\nYou don\'t know me! \"And\"? What more do you want tacked on to this? I turned myself into a pickle, and 9/11 was an inside job?\" What are you looking at, mother fucker! Get off the high road Summer. We all got pink eye because you wouldn\'t stop texting on the toilet.\r\n\r\nDon\'t be trippin dog we got you. I\'ll tell you how I feel about school, Jerry. It\'s a waste of time. Bunch of people runnin\' around bumpin\' into each other, got a guy up front says, \'2 + 2,\' and the people in the back say, \'4.\' Then the bell rings and they give you a carton of milk and a piece of paper that says you can go take a dump or somethin\'. I mean, it\'s not a place for smart people, Jerry. I know that\'s not a popular opinion, but that\'s my two cents on the issue. Oh, wow. That\'s an intense line of questioning, Snuffles This isn\'t Game of Thrones, Morty.', 'sdsad', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sdsad', '', '', '2018-01-25 22:01:20', '2018-01-26 00:01:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=54', 0, 'post', '', 0),
